{"tid":1901821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[網絡資訊戰] 黃色資訊圈 C.L.S., 藍色資訊圈 R.I.P.","createTime":"2020-02-28T04:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T07:52:50.000Z","uid":108757,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"901826be711d91f88a49bf6d94bd453196739989","tid":1901821,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"睇PO前先睇呢個︰<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒 : 唔好再去建制Page俾嬲嬲 thx<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901456</a><br />\n<br />\n網絡資訊戰最重要嘅一點係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Don't make stupid people famous</span></span><br />\n所以由今日開始，我地要有策略地處理資訊 (FB, youtube, 討論區等等)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃色資訊圈 C.L.S.</span></span><br />\nC - <strong>Comment</strong><br />\n留言支持同路人，多推PO。<br />\nL - <strong>Like</strong><br />\n讚好同路人言論，顯示人數優勢。<br />\nS - <strong>Share</strong> &amp; <strong>Subscribe</strong><br />\n將同路人資訊分享俾朋友，等大家一齊推。<br />\n訂閱頻道，令我地得到最新最快嘅資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">藍色資訊圈 R.I.P.</span></span><br />\nR - <strong>Report</strong><br />\n一日一檢舉，舉報藍絲失實言論、種族歧視及侵犯版權行為。等有關機構內部處理，唔好幫對家宣傳。<br />\nI - <strong>Ignore</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不回應、不理會、不俾嬲</span>，直接無視藍絲資訊，廢事幫人做宣傳。<br />\nP - <strong>Pause</strong><br />\n做任何野之前，首先要<span style=\"color: red;\">「暫停播放影片」</span>，唔好幫藍絲加view數。<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Don't make stupid people famous</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持自己人，無視On9仔！</span></span>"},{"pid":"db99210801293d87984c76c79598e2ac0686ca0e","tid":1901821,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"PISH<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6f3e785de0